.section *refid='rm' rm
.*
.ix 'rm'
.ix 'Formatting' 'rm'
.ix 'Margin' 'right'
.tag begin
.tdesc
Sets the right margin. The margin remains in effect until it is reset or until the end of the current page.
.tattrbs
.tattr margin=number
The number of character spaces. If the tag appears more than 'margin' character spaces into a line of text,
the margin becomes effective on the next line.
.tattrend
.tclass Formatting
.tcont Text, Formatting, In-line, Block, List-block
.tseealso
:HDREF refid='lm'.
.tag end

